24 packs of press on nails - 4 pieces of nail glue - 1 nail file How To Apply STEP 1: Cut your nails short to prevent them from upturning and not fitting the nails. STEP 2: Soak your hands in warm water to soften the cutin. And use the cuticle pusher to remove the dead skin around the nail. STEP 3: Polish your nails. Please be sure to polish the nail bed to make the press on nail fit better. STEP 4: Clean debris from nails. STEP 5: Wipe clean nails with alcohol cotton. Make sure the nail bed is dry and oil-free. STEP 6: Choose the press on nail that fits the size of your nail bed. STEP 7: Apply enough glue on press on nail or the natural nail. Please make sure that the glue is applied evenly. STEP 8: Fit the tail of the press on nail to your fingertips and slowly push it into the nail bed. STEP 9: Please press from the middle to the sides for 10-15 seconds. Make sure that there are no air bubbles remaining between the press on nail and the nail bed. STEP 10: Done. Please do not touch water within two hours. Tips of Apply - If you need a longer lasting, nail glue is your better choice. - If you want to reduce the damage to natural nails, nail tabs is your better choice. - Please do not touch water within two hours. - Please polish and clean the nail bed before apply.
